OL,3,CMum of drowned seven-year-old: 'I
OL,4,Cwouldn't wish it on my worst enemy'
OL,6,FThe mother of a seven-year-old girl
OL,7,Ffrom Doncaster who drowned in an
OL,8,Fincident at a hotel golf course says
OL,9,Fshe hopes lessons can be learned from
OL,10,Fthe death of her daughter.
OL,12,FNyla Bradshaw was found unresponsive
OL,13,Fin a pond at Owston Golf Course on 30
OL,14,FMarch after being taken to a nearby
OL,15,Fpark by a childminder.
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1         G1/6
OL,2,W,.!+.!/*%/*%,.!/*%/*%/"-$T,,,,,,,,,,,,,
