OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F335A1782134325
OL,3,CMum of drowned seven-year-old: 'I
OL,4,Cwouldn't wish it on my worst enemy'
OL,6,FRecalling the call she received at
OL,7,Fwork, her mother Hayley Beardsley told
OL,8,FITV News: "I made sure I got there as
OL,9,Fquickly as possible. It was about an
OL,10,Fhour and a half of not knowing. I
OL,11,Fcried my eyes out.
OL,13,F"We couldn't see her for ages and had
OL,14,Fto follow the ambulance to hospital
OL,15,Fand see her being wheeled out.
OL,17,F"They didn't want to give up but there
OL,18,Fwas nothing they could do. It was too
OL,19,Flate."
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1         G2/6
OL,2,W,.!+.!/*%/*%,.!/*%/*%/"-$T,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BYorks News CReg TV FThis Day
FL,336,330,260,120,000,100
PN,33503
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F335A1782134325
OL,3,CMum of drowned seven-year-old: 'I
OL,4,Cwouldn't wish it on my worst enemy'
OL,6,FNyla was non-verbal and autistic, but
OL,7,Fwas progressing well at school after
OL,8,Fthe family's initial struggle to find
OL,9,Fa suitable place for her additional
OL,10,Fneeds.
OL,12,FHer mum said: "She was very loud. She
OL,13,Fdidn't like loud noises but as long as
OL,14,Fshe was loud, she wasn't bothered."
OL,16,FMs Beardsley said children should be
OL,17,Ftaught to swim from an early age, but
OL,18,Falso wants further help for children
OL,19,Fwith disabilities.
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1         G3/6
OL,2,W,.!+.!/*%/*%,.!/*%/*%/"-$T,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BYorks News CReg TV FThis Day
FL,336,330,260,120,000,100
PN,33504
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F335A1782134325
OL,3,CMum of drowned seven-year-old: 'I
OL,4,Cwouldn't wish it on my worst enemy'
OL,6,FShe said: "Even if there was more put
OL,7,Fin place with funding, because one-to-
OL,8,Fone sessions are so expensive."
OL,10,FShe spoke of the kindness of the local
OL,11,Fcommunity. Nyla's funeral was partly
OL,12,Fpaid for by a crowdfunding appeal.
OL,14,F"Everything has changed," she added.
OL,15,F"There's a lot of reminders anywhere
OL,16,Fyou go. I don't think that will ever
OL,17,Fgo away. We have bad days, we have
OL,18,Fgood days.
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1         G4/6
OL,2,W,.!+.!/*%/*%,.!/*%/*%/"-$T,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BYorks News CReg TV FThis Day
FL,336,330,260,120,000,100
PN,33505
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F335A1782134325
OL,3,CMum of drowned seven-year-old: 'I
OL,4,Cwouldn't wish it on my worst enemy'
OL,6,F"No-one expects to lose a child,
OL,7,Fespecially at seven. Not really
OL,8,Fknowing her last moments was the
OL,9,Fhardest part. I wouldn't wish it on my
OL,10,Fworst enemy."
OL,12,FAhead of an expected weekend of hot
OL,13,Fweather and following a spate of open
OL,14,Fwater deaths in May, Hayley hopes that
OL,15,Fchildren will stay away from rivers,
OL,16,Flakes and ponds.
OL,18,FShe said: "Don't go in. You think it's
OL,19,Fsafe but it isn't. You can get caught
OL,20,Fin anything. Even if you're a strong
OL,21,Fswimmer it's not worth it."
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1         G5/6
OL,2,W,.!+.!/*%/*%,.!/*%/*%/"-$T,,,,,,,,,,,,,
